 Rocksteady的新蝙蝠侠游戏正在途中https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-new-batman-game-from-rocksteady-is-is-on-is-way-3836174?utm_source=rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-campaign=a-batman-batman-从摇滚乐开始的游戏Chris EdwardsFri, 07 Feb 2025 21:54:49 +0000 Film NewsGaming NewsNewsTV NewsBatman https://www.nme.com/?p=3836174 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆骑士" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>但是球迷可能会等一段时间</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-new-batman-game-from-rocksteady-is-on-its-way-3836174">从Rocksteady进行了一场新的蝙蝠侠游戏，该游戏</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆骑士" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/arkhamknight-credit-rocksteady@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/rocksteady-studios">Rocksteady</a>正在制作新的单人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/batman">蝙蝠侠</a>游戏，因为华纳兄弟公司（Warner Bros. Games）希望将重点放在其核心特许经营上。</p><p>华纳兄弟发现总裁兼首席执行官戴维·扎斯拉夫（David Zaslav）在经济电话会议上发表讲话，谈到了该公司面临的陷入困境的12个月，他们的冠军表现不佳，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league"><em>自杀小队：杀死正义联盟</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/super-smash-bros"><em>超级粉碎兄弟</em>。</a> - 风格的Brawler <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/multiversus"><em>Multivers</em></a> 。</p><p> “我们认识到[游戏业务]目前的潜力大大不足。” Zaslav说，在补充说华纳兄弟现在将仅在四场比赛中加倍：Hogwarts Legacy（续集已经在作品中），《凡人Kombat》，《权力的游戏》和DC，“尤其是蝙蝠侠”。</p><p> Zaslav补充说：“我们将开发工作集中在那些核心特许经营上，并以验证的工作室提高了我们的成功率。”</p><p>发现总裁兼首席执行官确认，Rocksteady“希望回到蝙蝠侠参加单人游戏”，但根据<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-07/warner-bros-video-game-division-faces-thin-slate-wonder-woman-issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>彭博社</em></a>的一份报告，由于其他游戏的陷入发展，任何此类标题都将在数年之内。 </p><figure id="attachment_3554786" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3554786" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3554786" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy.jpg" alt="蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆三部曲。图片来源：Rocksteady。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Batman-Arkham-Trilogy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3554786" class="wp-caption-text">蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆三部曲。图片来源：Rocksteady。</figcaption></figure><p>据说Monolith Productions的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/wonder-woman">《神力女超人》</a>游戏在去年年初重新启动和转换导演后遇到了麻烦。彭博社补充说，它已经成本超过1亿美元，距离发行距离还差不多。</p><p>同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/gotham-knights"><em>哥谭骑士</em></a>开发商WB Games蒙特利尔投掷了约翰·康斯坦丁的比赛，但从未获得过批准。 DCU Flash电影在票房表现不佳之后，还取消了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-flash">Flash</a>游戏。开发人员现在正在帮助其他头衔，据报道，正在为新<em>游戏游戏的</em>推销而努力。</p><p> <em>Xboxera</em>联合创始人尼克·贝克（Nick Baker）在X/Twitter帖子中表示，Rocksteady将返回做到这一点，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/new-batman-game-reportedly-in-the-pipeline-3796493">这是一场新的蝙蝠侠游戏的报道</a>。</p><p> “不确定哪个工作室人的梦想是，但我听说Rocksteady又回来了。我也认为索尼正在尝试钱笑，”他在回应《游戏奖》帐户时写道，要求人们为新的<em>蝙蝠侠</em>游戏命名他们的梦想开发人员。</p><p> Rocksteady是著名且受粉丝的<em>蝙蝠侠Arkham</em>系列游戏背后的工作室，该系列游戏使玩家走进了Caped Crusader的鞋子，并从各种恶棍中拯救了哥谭。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-new-batman-game-from-rocksteady-is-on-its-way-3836174">从Rocksteady进行了一场新的蝙蝠侠游戏，该游戏</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
